<body>
<div type="letter">
  
  
  <pb facs="1063243" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Viro Illustrissimo atque Celeberrimo
    <lb/><rs type="person">Nicolao Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>Math.</abbr> <abbr>Prof.</abbr> <rs type="place">Pat.</rs></salute>
  <lb/><rs type="person">Sebastianus Checotius</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></opener>
  <p><lb/>Amicitiam nostram vix dum satam, Vir Clarissime, iam robustam
    <lb/>adolescere, altioresque radices agere uti ex <rs type="letter">litteris</rs> tuis perspi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cio, plan<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> exulto. Quamobrem pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>fationibus, uti veros inter
    <lb/>sincerosque Amicos decet, ablegatis, ad tuam <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs> pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pero. Qua igitur in re nos consentientes volebas, iam ut
    <lb/>puto consensimus; animadverti enim ex eo quod scribis, aliud
    <lb/>tibi negatum, aliud affirmatum mihi esse: Itaque, in quo
    <lb/>ante<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> subdubius h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sitaveram, an scilicet aliqua in <rs type="place">Italic<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice></rs>
    <lb/>ad te <rs type="letter">epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice></rs> indicata tantum aliquantul<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> uberius expli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>canda forent, in eo, <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> sententi<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> accedente, plan<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> confir<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mor, dedique operam ut lectores mentem meam plenius asse<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>qui possint: Sed t<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>debat me, c<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> illa scriberem prolixitatis,
    <lb/>cum qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cumque vel levissima meditatio, non mediocri mihi
    <lb/>molestia luenda foret; nunc ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice>, summo Numinis bene<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ficio, sentio me sub Veris adventum in dies confirmari,
    <lb/>ut proptere<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> spes sit brevi futurum, n<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> et egregi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs type="biblio">soluti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>onis</rs> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in publicum iam-iam, ut scribis, exitur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>deliciis carere cogar. Exemplum, quod affers, virium se<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cund<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> ordinatas Logarithmic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> procedentium, confera<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mus ad norm<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <rs type="biblio">solutionis</rs> nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>; sitque proptere<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> 
    <pb facs="1063244" n="2"/> 
    <lb/><formula>AG</formula> tempus integri descensus; <formula>AB</formula> vis in principio, denotentque
    <lb/><figure/> ordinat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>ED</formula> vires in fine temporum <formula>AE</formula>, in e<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> de<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>scensuum lege, ut ratio temporis cuiuscumque de<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>scensus integri (symbola tua retineo) exprimatur
    <lb/>per sequentem functionem vis <formula>z</formula> agentis in eius<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dem descensus initio <choice><orig>(</orig><reg type="deleted"/></choice><choice><orig><formula>\frac{\text{Log:}\left(1+\sqrt{}1-\frac{a}{z}\right)-\text{Log:}\left(1-\sqrt{}1-\frac{a}{z}\right)}{\sqrt{}z}</formula></orig><reg><formula>\frac{\log\left(1+\sqrt{1}-\frac{a}{z}\right)-\log\left(1-\sqrt{1}-\frac{a}{z}\right)}{\sqrt{z}}</formula></reg></choice>
    <lb/>(qu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> ration<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> allato exemplo convenire demonstras.) Retineatur h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c
    <lb/>conditio, exponatque iam <formula>AC</formula> tempus Aliud, <formula>AB</formula> (<formula>z</formula>) vim aliam; <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>
    <lb/>quoniam functionem huius vis nov<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ingrediuntur ex hypothesi
    <lb/><formula>1</formula> subtangens Logarithmic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> <formula>a</formula><!-- Unterstrichene variable --> quantitates constantes, (quar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
    <lb/>proptere<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> nulla fit <hi rend="u">analoga substitutio</hi> <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> ad quas interim <hi rend="u">rela<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tio habetur</hi>, neque ad ea tant<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <hi rend="u">qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt eiusdem generis</hi> exten<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ditur, vides rem non iis conditionibus innixam, quas in assertio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ne nostra loco Antecedentis ponebamus, quid mir<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> igitur, si neque
    <lb/>id, quod consequens erat, obtineatur. Non multis tec<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice><supplied>,</supplied> Vir Doctissime<supplied>,</supplied>
    <lb/>opus est verbis. Ad hoc, aut simile gen<del>[...]</del><add>u</add>s, puto pertinent <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> alia
    <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> memoras exempla innumera ab assertione nostra aberran<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tia, quibus proptere<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> ad huiusmodi norm<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> exactis, inducti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>one veluti quodam, quale genus argumentationis nostris 
    <pb facs="1063245" n="3"/> 
    <lb/>iam usu receptum non ignoras, <rs type="biblio">solutionem</rs> nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> apud te,
    <lb/>quod vehementer cupio, purgatum iri confido. </p> <closer>Vale vir doctissime
      <lb/>tuique cultorem eximium ama. 
      <lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs type="place">Vicenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>a. d.</abbr> <date when="1719-03-21">12 <abbr>Kal.</abbr> <abbr>Apr.</abbr> 1719</date></dateline>
      <note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><foreign xml:lang="ger"><abbr>Empf.</abbr> den</foreign> <date when="1719-03-11">24.<hi rend="sup">ten</hi> Marti<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></date>.</note></closer>
  <pb facs="1063246" n="4" type="empty"/>
</div>
